   <category name='food'>

      <section name='spaceman'>

         <para number='1' comment='Buy food - Urban Spaceman - 453'>
         You press the touchpad on the bar and a sign lights up: please deposit ten groats. You put the correct coins into the appropriate slot, and your chili-dog appears from a serving hatch. It's hot... and very spicy... it appears to be made of meat, of some sort, but best not to enquire too closely! The cheese is bright orange and has the consistency of rubber. The whole thing fills you up but leaves you feeling slightly queasy.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Not enuff groats'>
         You press the touchpad on the bar and a sign lights up: please deposit ten groats. That's when you realize that you don't have ten groats - you are broke.
         </para>

      </section>

