      <section name='message'>

         <para number='1' comment='Player finds firestone'>
         As you enter the location you are drawn to a flickering smoky red gleam. It's a firestone, but it's already psychically imprinted with an image of the Magellan Society's crest. Obviously, it was left here for you to find. You prise it out of the wall, wrap it up to keep it safe and slip it into your pocket.
