      <section name='donut'>

         <para number='1' comment='Get donut - in loc 326 - 1'>
         You reach into the box and carefully extract a jelly donut. As you bite into it, the bright red jelly oozes out and smears all around your mouth.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Get donut - in loc 326 - 2'>
         You reach into the box and carefully extract a chocolate donut. The delicious chocolatey goodness makes you moan with pleasure as you munch your way through it.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Get donut - in loc 326 - 2'>
         You reach into the box and carefully extract a strawberry-frosted donut. The coating really does taste of real strawberries, even though it's probably been nowhere near a piece of fruit and is manufactured from all kinds of artificial flavorings.
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='Get donut - in loc 326 - 4'>
         You reach into the box and carefully extract a cream-filled donut. It is impossible to eat tidily - the cream spurts out with some pressure, landing on the desk. Guiltily, you finish up the donut, then wipe up the spilt cream.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='Get donut - in loc 326 - 5'>
         You reach into the box and carefully extract a sugar-covered donut. Each bite you take from it produces a cloud of powdered sugar which fills the air like a miniature blizzard. A thin layer lands on the operator's face, making him twitch and snort in his sleep, but the strong air conditioning in the room blows it away before long.
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='Get donut - in loc 326 - 6'>
         You reach into the box and carefully extract a green glowing donut. Odd - you didn't know donuts could be luminous. Biting into the donut you realize the green isn't because it is mint-flavored, or lime, or even pistachio - it's a radioactive donut! Oh dear! You hastily discard it, and hope it hasn't done you too much harm.
         </para>

         <para number='7' comment='Get donut - in loc 326 - 7'>
         You reach into the box and carefully extract a donut. Except that it's not a donut - for some reason, there is a piece of jam rolypoly in the box! Wonder how that got there? Oh well, it tastes almost as good as a donut.
         </para>

